reviewText: Couldn't understand it, did not have subtitle option

great series, loved watching it as a kid, brought back many happy memories, highly recommended, just disappointed that it only had selected episodes, since I never got to watch them all, was not familiar with the some of the episodes selected and was lost as to what was happening and why
Nice to see british soaps once again
the plot is to slow. It was boring. I didn't like it period!!!. I wouldn't recommend it to anyone,sorry. I love English comody and drama,I was very disappointed.
